OL,3,C'I've never seen it as dire':
OL,4,CDevelopers outline housebuilding
OL,5,Cobstacles
OL,7,FA lack of adequate wastewater
OL,8,Finfrastructure is the biggest obstacle
OL,9,Fto housebuilding in Northern Ireland,
OL,10,Faccording to a report from the Royal
OL,11,FInstitution of Chartered Surveyors.
OL,13,FIt comes as the number of new homes
OL,14,Fbeing built has reached a 60-year low.
OL,15,FLast year, just 5,000 were built, with
OL,16,Fdevelopers saying that figure needs to
OL,17,Fdouble to keep up with demand.
