OL,3,C'I've never seen it as dire':
OL,4,CDevelopers outline housebuilding
OL,5,Cobstacles
OL,7,F"I've been through a property crash,
OL,8,FCovid, a banking crisis and I've never
OL,9,Fseen it as dire as it is now", said
OL,10,FConor Mulligan from Build Homes NI.
OL,12,F"I've been talking to other developers
OL,13,Fwho have been in this game for 40
OL,14,Fyears and they're just talking about
OL,15,Fclosing down or easing off production
OL,16,Fbecause it's just too difficult at the
OL,17,Fmoment to supply houses," he added.
