OL,3,C'I've never seen it as dire':
OL,4,CDevelopers outline housebuilding
OL,5,Cobstacles
OL,7,FAs the supply of new homes has
OL,8,Fdecreased, the number of people on
OL,9,Fsocial housing waiting lists has risen
OL,10,Fdramatically, with those living in
OL,11,Ftemporary accommodation doubling over
OL,12,Fthe last five years.
OL,14,FAccording to Seamus Leheny from the NI
OL,15,FFederation of Housing Associations, it
OL,16,Fis time to label the problem properly.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/8
