OL,3,C'I've never seen it as dire':
OL,4,CDevelopers outline housebuilding
OL,5,Cobstacles
OL,7,F"In Northern Ireland, we've been a
OL,8,Flittle bit shy about mentioning the
OL,9,Fwords 'housing crisis', but we look at
OL,10,FDublin, we look at London, we look at
OL,11,Fother places in the UK. We really need
OL,12,Fto take this head-on and solve this
OL,13,Fnow," he said.
OL,15,FTo address the problem, Mr Mulligan is
OL,16,Fcalling on the Executive to not "rule
OL,17,Fanything out" and "look at all
OL,18,Fsolutions", including the water
OL,19,Fcharges.
