OL,3,C'I've never seen it as dire':
OL,4,CDevelopers outline housebuilding
OL,5,Cobstacles
OL,7,F"When you see possible water charges
OL,8,Fof #200 or #300 a year, or you're
OL,9,Fsaying to people to pay #500 more a
OL,10,Fmonth in rent, people will soon start
OL,11,Fto weight things up," he said.
OL,13,FMeanwhile, a Department for
OL,14,FInfrastructure spokesperson has said:
OL,15,F"Despite operating in a difficult
OL,16,Ffinancial environment for a number of
OL,17,Fyears due to underfunding and
OL,18,Fausterity by the British Government,
OL,19,FNI Water has been provided by the
OL,20,FDepartment with #0.5 billion of public
OL,21,Fmoney this financial year.
