OL,3,C'I've never seen it as dire':
OL,4,CDevelopers outline housebuilding
OL,5,Cobstacles
OL,7,F"NI Water was also allocated an
OL,8,Fadditional #19.5 m during October
OL,9,Fmonitoring, specifically to address
OL,10,Fconstraints in wastewater
OL,11,Finfrastructure and to unlock capacity
OL,12,Ffor housing connections. This funding
OL,13,Fwill lead to additional capacity for
OL,14,Fsome 2,300 new properties to connect
OL,15,Fto the sewerage system.
